scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: The ISDA Schedule begins at line 262 ("SCHEDULE to the ISDA MASTER AGREEMENT") and continues through the end of the detailed Schedule provisions, which conclude at line 701 (the end of Part 5(29)). The following sections (Annexures, Confirmations, and Credit Support Annexes) are not part of the Schedule itself but are separate documents or annexes. This span covers only the Schedule and not the standard pre-print, CSA annexes, or Confirmations, as requested.
